Package com.hds.aw.auto.reportingApi.sdk.interfaces.admin

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdminReport  
    HighQuotaUsageReport
    Reports all users in the system or specified profile(s) near or above their allocated quota.
    OrphanedUserReport
    Reports all users in the system that are not a member of any profile.
    ProfileOverridesReport
    Returns all users in the system or specified profile that have settings that have been overridden, and reports the overridden settings.
    SystemStorageReport
    Reports the amount of data stored in the HCP Anywhere system.
    TeamFoldersReport
    Reports all existing Team Folders in the system.
    UserAuthProviderAccessReport
    Reports the external state in the authentication provider of users in the system or specified profile(s).
    UserAwAccessReport
    Reports the HCP Anywhere access status of all users in the HCP Anywhere system or specified profile(s).
    UserDevicesReport
    Reports all registered HCP Anywhere devices of users in the system or specified profile(s).
    UserLastAccessReport
    Reports the last access time for a user in the system or specified profile(s).
    UserStorageReport
    Reports the amount of data stored in the HCP Anywhere system by users in the specified profile(s).
